name: AI Floki
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
AI Floki aims to revolutionize the crypto currency industry by integrating advanced AI technology into its ecosystem. Unlike many other meme coins, AI Floki provides practical utility through AI image and language generation, as well as AI staking capabilities for traders. The development team behind AI Floki is constantly working to improve the technology, making it even smarter and more advanced.
AI Floki follows in the footsteps of Floki Inu in giving utility to its ecosystem via artificial intelligence, rather than just a meme coin.
